# Project Conventions

## 1. Chat Language

Always respond in Spanish in chat conversations.

## 2. Artifacts Language

All files and documentation you write or modify must be in English:

- Source code (comments, variable names, strings for i18n)
- Documentation (README, docs, specs)
- Configuration files and their comments

## 3. BMAD Method

Prefer BMAD workflows when the task matches. Consult `_bmad/_config/workflow-manifest.csv` for available workflows. Examples:

- Product brief → bmad-create-product-brief
- PRD → bmad-create-prd
- Quick changes → bmad-quick-spec, bmad-quick-dev
- Sprint planning → bmad-sprint-planning
- etc.
